latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Crafted for the future you, with premium materials, industry leading scratch resistance glass, latest heart monitor, stainless steel body sealed with titanium screws and coated with ultra hard scratch resistant PVD, the all new Moto 360 is ready for the future you. 

I love it because it lasts two days on a single 60min charge 

I don’t need to worry about it getting wet in the rain, because of its water resistant capabilities be it shower, pool or sea.

With cutting edge data and sensors, it keeps track of my well being, with advance heart rate monitor, sleep and fitness activities tracker aides in keeping me in my top notch state all the time. 

Convenience is now in your smartwatch, the Moto360 is powered by WearOS by Google and has all the apps you need from paying your bills with Gpay to navigation with Maps and Messaging with Whatsapp. 

And with nine different faces to choose from you have more reason to style your watch to match your lifestyle and the occasion.

Check out the link in the bio! You wont regret it.

latestPosts.caption:
Just checked into paradise at Holiday Inn, Kolkata and every moment felt like a summer dream! 🌇

From the cozy, spacious rooms to the lavish buffet spread, the stay was nothing short of perfect. The rooftop pool gave me the coolest escape, and the breathtaking bird’s eye view of the airport – with planes soaring just above – was surreal! 🛬

Evenings were best spent at Urban, the in-house bar, sipping on refreshing mocktails, cocktails, and an array of summer coolers that kept the vibes alive 🍹🍸

And here’s the cherry—or should I say mango—on top: their “Aam-azing Utsav”! A festive celebration of mangoes with an irresistible spread of desserts crafted by their brilliant chefs. Sweet, tangy, and utterly divine!

Can’t help but appreciate each and every moment spent here. Holiday Inn Kolkata truly knows how to make summer special
